---
title: Pasta
description: Classic pasta dish with tomato sauce and fresh basil.
---

Boil @pasta{400%g} according to package directions until al dente, then drain.

Heat @olive-oil{2%tbsp} in a large pan and cook @garlic{3%cloves} until fragrant, about 1 minute.

Add @tomato-sauce{500%ml} to the pan with @garlic and simmer for 5 minutes to let flavors meld.

Toss the drained pasta with the sauce and top with fresh @basil{1%bunch} and @parmesan{100%g} before serving.
